relation: Bird thing from an EB64 screenshot. And you know, that screenshot's pretty blurry at least, the one I looked at was this one. I eventually happened upon a clearer shot and I must say that I was pleasantly surprised with some of the guesswork I had to do.

Inspired by Gonmon's Boogie Tent I was thinking that the original game tent could have looked more interesting had it had a yellow-purple striped pattern. Plus, i was always a little miffed that all you saw were the mouth and eyes of the Boogie Tent, so I drew this up.

"But it's the Major one you want to fight." I'd started this one pondering the idea that the Psychic Psycho wasn't so much on fire, but that his suit has become a sort of psyonically-generated living flame. Well, I goofed somehwere along the way in drawing it and saved it as a png and its layers weren't preserved... Oh well. I abandonned it but submitted it anyway, 'cause it still was looking kinda' cool.
